data.description: This property boasts a huge corner lot with a nice size backyard and a covered patio, perfect for entertaining your guests. It's equipped with new carpet downstairs, new roof, new air conditioning units (2), a new water heater, water softener, and a water filtration system, ensuring your comfort and convenience. With raised ceilings and an open floor plan, the interior feels airy and inviting. The home comes with a lifetime warranty on foundation support. All bedrooms are upstairs. Come and see this gem & call it your home sweet home.
